Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(955,658)}みち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚才来 干什么去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来这边 给你占了个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:44.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くだけてものを　おもふころかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我心向伊处 肠断情亦摧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:51.94,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}なにはがた　みじかきあしの　ふしのまも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:51.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「苇生难波滩 节短聚益稀」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手误
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好少见 方向完全错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一场比赛的记忆还留在脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一旦变得疲劳 忘记就比记住还要困难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛也已经是第六场比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么集中精神 还是会出现失误的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 重新确认一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 重新确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「春深」已经出现过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.01,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,658)}はなの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以「山风」在听到「はな」时就要进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.85,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,658)}はなさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「冷山」则因为「九重」还没读到 所以要谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,658)}もろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,658)}もも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「筑波」已经出现过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:33.73,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,658)}つく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以「寒夜」在听到「つ」时就要去抢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.94,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,658)}つき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「晴春」和「久别」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.48,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,658)}ひさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.48,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,658)}ひとは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为「莫道」还没出现所以要小心手误
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.98,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,658)}ひとも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「木津」有友牌的「守卒」在 所以要放手进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,658)}みかの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,658)}みかき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「陆奥」和敌阵左边的「雄岛」 也差不多要被读到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.99,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,658)}みち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.99,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,658)}みせ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「世间」因为有友牌的「粗缆」在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.25,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,658)}よのなかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.25,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(815,658)}よのなかは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要一边注意一边使用围手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪张都要抢下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「离多」因为「大江」和「初入」都读到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.38,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,658)}あふこ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.38,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,658)}おほえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.38,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,658)}おほけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到「おほ」就要进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要抢到敌阵左边的「情冷」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.01,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(815,658)}おも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「促织」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.26,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,658)}きり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为「初春」和「昔时」都读到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.26,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,658)}きみがためは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.26,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,658)}きみがためを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以变成了一字决定牌 听到「き」就要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「激流」一定要抢到 不能被对方守住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.27,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,658)}せ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「芙蓉」和「苇生」已经读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.77,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,658)}ながか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.77,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,658)}なにはが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去进攻「仲夏」 然后倒回来抢己阵的「羁旅」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.65,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,658)}なつ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.65,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,658)}なにはえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑麻痹了 除了前面什么都看不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看前面就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:30.97,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あはでこのよを　すぐしてよとや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「怨君心何忍 残生会无期」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.22,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つきみれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「寒夜眺冷月…」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想着快点 再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可手臂却不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动得快一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子已经动起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动得更快一点啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 赢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户田学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 你成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是富士崎的高三生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只输三张 已经干得很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么跟画一样标准的失望状…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不甘心吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚军是最不甘心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的付出…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不配让我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心有不甘就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使成为大人 要面对失败也是很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那些孩子们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有互相安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要赶新干线 动作快一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要落下东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真早啊 上午就开始练习跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是田径部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌…歌留多部?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有兴趣了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加过大赛以后 我想大家都能看到自己的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家都同样需要的 就是体力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算累了 集中力也不能中断
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了赢下冠军 能连续比赛10小时的体力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们利用暑假来锻炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为我在实力上会输给真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我的目标也是拿下B级的冠军」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被拉开距离…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追上去!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是对手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡着了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 睡了10分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被肉包小子紧追不舍啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几天…一直梦到诗畅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.15,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\frz261.162\fad(235,0)\move(963,425,959,447,100,1290)}还有雪人丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗畅…是指现在的女王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在录像上看到了 强得吓人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很吓人 所以才叫她「诗畅」的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全国大会上 明明也见到新了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是新却没在梦中出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梦以外的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了 你说是谁来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总算来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栗山老师 请让我加入福井南云会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:54.06,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くもがくれにし　よはのつきかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「犹恨会时短 如月隐云间」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.48,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はるのよの…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「春深夜苦短…」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.61,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たかさごの…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「繁樱缀高岭…」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.53,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このたびは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「匆匆赴羁旅…」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多的秋季将会来临
